videos.description: Fighting Irish's Bonzie Colson fights for the rebound and makes a great turnaround jumper.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Colson hustles for board and bucket

videos.description: DePaul's Justin Roberts shows his handle and bounce passes it to Jaylen Butz who gets the ball stuck between the basket and backboard.
videos.headline: Blue Devils' Roberts with nice handles

videos.description: Blue Demons' Eli Cain throws it up to Tre'Darius McCallum for a dunk.
videos.headline: DePaul's McCallum throws down alley-oop dunk

videos.description: Blue Demons' Eli Cain misses a three pointer, but grabs the loose ball and makes a sweet layup using the backboard.
videos.headline: DePaul's Cain makes great use of backboard

videos.description: DePaul's Max Strus denies Notre Dame's Martinas Geben a layup by swatting the ball away.
videos.headline: Blue Demons' Strus with great block

videos.description: Blue Demon's Devin Gage makes a great steal, and tosses it up to Max Stus who blows the jam.
videos.headline: DePaul's Strus misses easy alley-oop

videos.description: DePaul's Devin Gage jumps up extremely high to intercept a pass, and makes a sweet layup that doesn't count because of a foul.
videos.headline: Blue Demons' Gage with great steal

videos.description: Notre Dame's Temple Gibbs drains in a three point jumper assisted by Bonzie Colson.
videos.headline: Fighting Irish's Gibbs with wide open 3-pointer

videos.description: Temple Gibbs extends Fighting Irish's lead with his fourth 3-pointer of the game.
videos.headline: Notre Dame's Gibbs hits another 3-pointer

videos.description: Blue Demons' Eli Cain drives it to the basket, and slams it home.
videos.headline: DePaul's Cain with one-handed dunk
